125cc456dfaa17f2.poster.avif?t=1773214650\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421520/extras/98a9db4faf2e6f34125cc456dfaa17f2.webm?t=1773214650\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421520/extras/98a9db4faf2e6f34125cc456dfaa17f2.mp4?t=1773214650\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ENVIRONMENT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the randomly generated environment in each game. Avoid asteroids and explosives while evading the danger of enemy turrets. Overcome various anomalies, including temporal fields, electrical storms, wormholes, and more. Utilize the strategic advantage of an electrical storm to ambush your opponents or quickly escape danger by traversing through a nearby wormhole!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421520/extras/bee08fe61895c95c616dc3d3ef75d0be.poster.avif?t=1773214650\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421520/extras/bee08fe61895c95c616dc3d3ef75d0be.webm?t=1773214650\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421520/extras/bee08fe61895c95c616dc3d3ef75d0be.mp4?t=1773214650\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAME MODES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play 3 different game modes in single-player or multiplayer, each available with Bots and in Teams or Free-for-All, with adjustable map sizes. Defeat as many enemies as possible in Deathmatch, be the last to survive in the closing zone of One Life, or fight for control of the battlefield in Zone Control!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421520/extras/02d76aab89465b2ae0e4bda2cee7df3c.poster.avif?t=1773214650\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421520/extras/02d76aab89465b2ae0e4bda2cee7df3c.webm?t=1773214650\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421520/extras/02d76aab89465b2ae0e4bda2cee7df3c.mp4?t=1773214650\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ACHIEVEMENTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete various achievements to unlock in-game avatar borders to show off in multiplayer!</p>",
